# Account Deletion Request - Sleep Juicy

**Last updated: October 30, 2025**

## How to Request Account Deletion

To request deletion of your Sleep Juicy account and associated data, please follow these steps:

### Step 1: Send an Email
Send an email to **MarcusBlanchar@gmail.com** with the subject line: **"Account Deletion Request"**

### Step 2: Include Your Information
In your email, please include:
- Your registered email address
- Your name (as it appears in the app)
- Confirmation that you want to permanently delete your account

### Step 3: Confirmation
We will send you a confirmation email within 48 hours to verify your request.

### Step 4: Deletion Process
Once confirmed, your account and all associated data will be permanently deleted within **30 days**.

---

## What Data Will Be Deleted

When you request account deletion, the following data will be permanently deleted:

### Personal Information
- ✅ Email address
- ✅ Name
- ✅ Age and gender
- ✅ Profile information

### Sleep Data
- ✅ All sleep logs and sleep events
- ✅ Sleep patterns (bedtime, wake time, sleep duration)
- ✅ Sleep quality metrics
- ✅ Sleep goals and preferences

### Quiz and Profile Data
- ✅ Onboarding quiz answers
- ✅ Detailed sleep quiz answers
- ✅ Chronotype information
- ✅ Additional notes and information

### Account Data
- ✅ Authentication credentials
- ✅ User preferences and settings
- ✅ AI chat history

---

## What Data May Be Retained

The following data may be retained for legal or security purposes:

- **Log data**: Error logs and crash reports (anonymized, no personal identifiers)
- **Legal records**: Any data required to comply with legal obligations
- **Security records**: Data related to security incidents or fraud prevention

This retained data will be anonymized and will not be associated with your personal information.

---

## Data Retention Period

- **Account deletion**: Completed within 30 days of your confirmed request
- **Anonymized logs**: Retained for up to 90 days for security and debugging purposes
- **Legal records**: Retained as required by law

---

## Alternative: Delete Data Within the App

You can also delete individual sleep logs directly within the Sleep Juicy app:
1. Go to the Sleep Log page
2. Tap the "Delete" button on any sleep log entry
3. Confirm deletion

**Note**: Deleting individual sleep logs does not delete your account. To delete your entire account and all data, you must send an email request as described above.

---

## Questions?

If you have any questions about account deletion or data privacy, please contact us at **MarcusBlanchar@gmail.com**.

---

**Sleep Juicy** is committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring your data is handled responsibly.

